@node "INSTAL" "Instalación de newNET"
@next "RTFM"
@prev "REQUI"


                            INSTALATION


     The instalation  of  @{b}newNET@{ub} is quite easy. Only is needed to
    copy the newNET file to your SYS:C/ drawer and the  language
    file s/newNET.ENGLISH to your SYS:S/ drawer @{b}*renaming*@{ub} it as
    newNET.LANG

    If this is very difficult for you or newNET doesn't work  as
    must be waited,   you can use the included  installer script
    @{b}install-newNET@{ub} from its own icon.

     This installer will check that you have correctly installed
    all the files that @{b}newNET@{ub} @{"REQUIRES" link "REQUI" 0} to work.
@endnode

